Optimization of D-strip models

A D-strip model consists of D-strips Di , parameterized by xi (u, v), and joined together along edge curves pi (u) as shown by Fig. 4. We want to work with B-spline surfaces, so we let X 3 pi (u) := B (u â j) bi,j , (4)
